Texts.Eng: Bring the ^orange;Contaminated Water^reset; to ^green;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
I just can't figure out how to make the ^orange;contaminated water^reset; for some of my chemical stock. Can you help and make me some in a ^orange;centrifuge^reset;?
When you are able to, ^green;upgrade to an advanced centrifuge^reset; to really step up your lab game! Oh and be sure to keep your Contaminated water, you might need it.
